hopobject.body: What sort of music do you listen to? motrin before oral surgery You don't know why they dropped out of school, maybe there was problems at home, if they even had a home, maybe they had a tragedy in the family, mother died, father died or sickness with nobody to help them, had to drop out to take care of their younger siblings and never got the chance to finish school or get a GED. Maybe they need to benefits to help them get their GED to get a better job. Don't always assume that their end results was just to get the benefits.
